{"tid":1742444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"POLY一役點解係輸？我覺得係贏喎","createTime":"2019-11-20T20:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T00:07:43.000Z","uid":31920,"like":11,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a3540e4218965130c648cd938538a50054e018de","tid":1742444,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:19:41.000Z","msg":"歷史上邊一場戰爭係無損傷？<br />\n<br />\n今次一戰如果格硬要講輸，係輸互屌，屌守咩城<br />\n<br />\n無錯今次係失去左一D手足<br />\n<br />\n但同時激發咗一堆和理非勇武嘅心<br />\n<br />\n而且都救到一大批手足已經係好好好好不錯<br />\n<br />\n有人話今次圍城無左起碼一半勇武<br />\n<br />\n咁18號果晚出黎既係？<br />\n<br />\n18號果晚隨時係無不反下最多人願意出黎既一次&ldquo;遊行／抗爭&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n根本係一次大團結，凝聚返有良知既香港人<br />\n<br />\n所以，POLY一役根本就係贏<br />\n<br />\n要輸，只係輸左吹失敗風，而少左嘅士氣"},{"pid":"0bceccbc6bb8666700739cb33c7cf4f38b9fdab4","tid":1742444,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:23:49.000Z","msg":"不過我唔明<br />\n<br />\n搬返哂D磚去路兩邊係做乜撚"},{"pid":"7e43c98214695cee9d712c38b073659ab60b20a3","tid":1742444,"uid":167828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:24:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f6027fb1b5d84b16932ecb3c2e077191343e0cb","tid":1742444,"uid":206594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:24:50.000Z","msg":"咁講法邊場仗唔係贏<br />\n唔肯檢討同贏國成日話自己贏有咩分別<br />\n今次唯一可取嘅係留得返啖氣<br />\n以戰養戰<br />\n唔捨身去營救大家士氣仲低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f2cc9752ac5a0990e11fa252d1cbd1bd37cb90","tid":1742444,"uid":79562,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:25:47.000Z","msg":"為咗救幾百人 犧牲成千人<br />\n<br />\n零戰果 而幾百人入面多人投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一陣又有人話我分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbfbeae0c74331d22eb63c0d5b892a7633b41b6","tid":1742444,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7e43c98214695cee9d712c38b073659ab60b20a3","tid":1742444,"uid":167828,"like":5,"dislike"